1
00:00:00,250 --> 00:00:02,580
My heart almost jumped out of my chest!

2
00:00:02,750 --> 00:00:03,920
Isn't that a good thing?

3
00:00:03,920 --> 00:00:04,920
Not at all.

4
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:07,330
I thought my mouth was going to
jump out of my heart.

5
00:00:07,630 --> 00:00:08,630
You got that backwards.

6
00:00:08,830 --> 00:00:10,460
A mouth jumping out of a heart.

7
00:00:10,630 --> 00:00:12,540
A talking heart?
That's terrifying.

8
00:00:12,960 --> 00:00:14,670
A heart jumping out of your mouth
is pretty terrifying too.

9
00:00:14,790 --> 00:00:15,790
Tell me about it.

10
00:00:15,960 --> 00:00:17,080
Gross.

11
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:19,500
So gross.

12
00:00:19,670 --> 00:00:21,080
Anyway.

13
00:00:25,880 --> 00:00:27,330
You wouldn't understand.

14
00:00:27,330 --> 00:00:29,210
You just don't get it, Kaede.

15
00:00:29,330 --> 00:00:31,210
He's a superstar!

16
00:00:31,290 --> 00:00:33,460
Idols are meant to be admired.

17
00:00:33,580 --> 00:00:34,580
They're like works of art.

18
00:00:34,750 --> 00:00:36,040
The highest form of art.

19
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:37,920
They're untouchable.

20
00:00:38,290 --> 00:00:41,080
You can't touch the exhibits
in a museum, can you?

21
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:45,830
The more perfect the piece,
the more you should admire it quietly from a distance.

22
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:47,540
Are you talking about me?

23
00:00:48,710 --> 00:00:49,710
Hey.

24
00:00:49,790 --> 00:00:51,500
Um, this is...

25
00:00:51,670 --> 00:00:53,580
the freshman classroom.

26
00:00:53,670 --> 00:00:54,830
What's a sophomore doing here?

27
00:00:54,830 --> 00:00:56,420
Just came to hang out.

28
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:58,040
Huh? Am I not allowed?

29
00:00:58,710 --> 00:01:00,580
Well, I guess there's no rule against it.

30
00:01:00,580 --> 00:01:02,540
In that case, I'm joining
your snack party!

31
00:01:02,710 --> 00:01:05,210
Oh, hey.
I wanted to ask you something.

32
00:01:06,710 --> 00:01:08,040
Hey!

33
00:01:14,830 --> 00:01:16,290
Do they hate me?

34
00:01:16,750 --> 00:01:18,460
I don't think so.
